OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late evening
OL,7,Fsunshine on offer, but cloudier for
OL,8,Fcoastal areas of Argyll. Remaining dry
OL,9,Fovernight with mostly clear skies but
OL,10,Fcloudier around the coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry day and mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fnear the coasts with some bright or
OL,14,Fsunny intervals. Further inland will
OL,15,Fsee clearer skies and plenty of
OL,16,Fsunshine, feeling warm here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
